---+++ Accomodation

We do not have a particular block of rooms set apart for this event, but we recommend the following [[http://www.uchicago.edu/about/accommodations.shtml][hotels in downtown Chicago]]. In particular, Fairfield Inn &amp; Suites by Marriott and Doubletree(Magnificent Mile) offer very good location and rates. (please ask for the discounted UChicago rate when calling). For students, or people interested in staying closer to the University campus and the location of the event, we suggest the [[http://ihouse.uchicago.edu/][International House]]. Note: downtown is about 10 miles from the campus and you&#39;ll need to arrange transportation to and from the event. (a cab ride is $20, a bus ride is $2 or you could rent a car and park in the nearby garage at 55th &amp; Ellis Ave for $20/day or free in the street, if you come early and you&#39;re lucky to find a spot).

